{"title":"农场小景（外一首）","authors":["未名"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":10,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"农场小景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未名"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藏族人民来学七吋步犁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲把孩子背在背上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子比在家里还不安宁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽在背上乱幌乱嚷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是孩子又想吃糌粑？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是呆在背上不舒畅？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问问孩子什么都不是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又为什么会这样……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子只扒出来脑袋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把母亲学扶犁的样子望望；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子，安静些，尽望些什么，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你也想看会，帮帮妈的忙？"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}